{
  "stem": "9503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Railroads were-- were destroyed, so we would be on a-- a-- a train for you know, a day, and then we'd go back on trucks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't remember where we slept, but it took weeks to get back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my mother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had my book.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember anything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And again, I don't remember hygiene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do remember that we went out in the meadows for-- for toileting needs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't remembered any hygiene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I do remember, at one point, we traveled in a cattle car, and this time the door was open.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the car moved very slowly, maybe because of the way the tracks were at the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had enough room to have-- make ourselves a bed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was only-- it was children and mothers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think that was all that was on the-- on the-- in this car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we came to a station in Germany, and there were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was sitting in this open doorway with my legs dangling out, and it was safe to do that because the car didn't move that fast.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we came into the station, and all of a sudden we were surrounded with German ex-soldiers, ex-German soldiers, whatever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they wanted-- they were begging for food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I got a-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I lost it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I started kicking, scratching, and my mother had to pull me in so that I wouldn't be, you know, hurt in-- in return.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somebody said to my mother that you-- you-- in German, you shouldn't talk that much hatred into your child.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my mother said, I have never talked hatred into her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It comes with, you know, the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember emotions about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
